snippet.title: Disaster Arms (Steam Announcement Trailer)
snippet.description:
BOSS RUSH IS BACK!!!

As Earth reaches the precipice of apocalypse, a lone boy with vengeful eyes rushes towards KaiserCorps, the leading authority on weapons technologies and the epicenter of an alien rampage. 

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3462730/Disaster_Arms__Impact_Project_BAHN/
